############  Install & Build  ##############

Add the following line to your ~/.bashrc:

  source ~/OpenFOAM/OpenFOAM-1.6-ext/etc/bashrc
+ source /path/to/CombustionAddons/bashrc

Please adjust the paths in CombustionAddons/bashrc according to your local installation.

Dependencies:
 * Cuba 3.0

CUBA 3.0
========
Compile with:
$ CFLAGS=-fPIC ./configure --prefix=/home/hannes/Programme/Cuba-3.0/platforms/linux64GccDPOpt
